      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WEST ON SIDNEY (2) is better than last start when fourth (29.99) in a Special conditions SF at The Meadows over 525m. Boasts a strong record from this draw with two wins and two minor placings from five starts. Can atone. ICONIC JET (6) is worth forgiving for his last effort when fifth (28.31) at Mandurah over 488m. Form here sound including six wins. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. FLEETWOOD KAZAK (3) had been in great form but missed the frame latest when eighth (28.33) in a Free For All at Mandurah. Generally fast into stride but was shuffled back from the tricky draw last time. Solid record here at the distance winning seven races. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Has ability and is one of the better chances. ICONIC GUESS (7) comes into calculations after placing most recently.",
